<div class="p">Ope' the arcade window, Ope' the door inset</div>
<div class="p">In the public archway causing yet</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Tremolo in the knocking hand,</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A trembling, later opening;</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Each finger turning to remand</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The likely act of perishing.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">Lone reluctant fingers, ’Lone the fingers rob,</div>
<div class="p">Scrimping on as a halfway willing mob.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Truckle away the letters, you five;</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Dishonor thus their coffin bed;</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Excited riffle for a live</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Companion to the blanching dead.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">Lightning joy—the letter; Lightning set the name,</div>
<div class="p">Scripted like to a raven all aflame.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Ciphers a human hand had writ</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; To sink and burn with blushing tone,</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; As cherry juice beside the pit:</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A charcoal fire overblown.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">Haste, O foolish fingers, Haste and join your cause;</div>
<div class="p">Damp the moment not with heedless pause.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Rapidly break the joining line</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; That marks the crimping of a plane,</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The sacrificial edge, or chine—</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; This breaking, paper, fall a-twain.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">Tease the viscous letter, Tease it from its sheath;</div>
<div class="p">Draw it out from jagged paper teeth.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Annex the folded paper ream;</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Unfold the o'erbent drapery;</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Beat down the low ambitious seam;</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Disrobe misguided modesty.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">Read the goodly letter, Read its lines at last;</div>
<div class="p">As you read will time dare fly you past?</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Eagerly outrun the well-known script,</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Then dwell about the signature:</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; And risk a sojourn in the crypt;</div>
<div class="p" id="small">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; To words above, a ligature.</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="p">Then turn—in grateful recompense</div>
<div class="p">Relatch the vessel of your mood.</div>
<div class="p">Then turn—completed reverence</div>
<div class="p">In ending becks beatitude.</div>
